description: It’s almost as if they’re begging us to open our eyes... are you connecting the dots? We all knew 2020 was going to be a big year and it can only go one of two ways... the Ushering in of the Great awakening aka False “controlled” Awakening (I hope not) or the beginning of the End of our freedom as we know it. Is that a double negative possibly, but there’s a third option, Unmatrix yourself and go within yourself to find the Father, spiritual death is underway, will they take yours? #billgates #corona #virus #coronamemes #covid19 #statistics #billgatesisevil #trump #qontrolledopposition #flatearthawakening
